body.description: Cool USB 2.0 Flash Drive, a Perfect Gift for Your Family or Friends It is more suitable for people with thick wrists, otherwise it may fall out. Why choose our USB drive? 1. Portable, lightweight, and cool style, very durable, easy to carry; 2. Convenient: No need for power supply, no need drive, only plug in; 4. Allows you to wear it on your wrist, keeping important documents within reach 5. Store and protect photos, videos, and important work files with our USB Flash Drive; 6. Durable solid-state storage: Use an A-class chip, which can be erased repeatedly for 100,0000 times; 7. Support Win 98 / 8/ 7 / 10 / ME / 2000 / XP / Vista, Mac OS / Linux; 8. Support PC Mode: All brands of Desktop PCs, laptops, and other consumer electronic devices with USB interfaces, etc. Specification: USB Interface: USB 2.0 Material: Metal + leather Environment Temperature: -40C - +70C Storage Temperature: -50C - +80C USB Service Voltage: 4.5V-5.5V Storage Lifetime: More than 10 years Net Weight: 25g Hardware Requirement: Suitable for computers with standard USB A interface, not for mobile phones Package Include: 1 x USB 2.0 Flash Drive Note: Why does the actual capacity of the USB flash drive not match the correct capacity? Flash memory vendors use decimal arithmetic: 1MB = 1000KB,1G = 1000MB calculated, the operating system uses binary arithmetic: 1MB = 1024KB,1GB = 1024MB, So there are some differences between the display capacity and nominal capacity of flash memory product 64GB is about 57.8-60GB
